<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan>, wir senden czu euch Hansen
                                <expan>Erelbecke<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        dyener, mit euch czu reden von Jobsen Pelers, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
                        gescholn, und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> dyener wegen, die darümb czu
                        Holfelt bekümert worden sein. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc. ut in
                                <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
                        Francisci.</ab>
</div>
